reviewTitle: Bad experience. The service is so bad.
reviewContent: Bad experience. The service is so bad and the food is not worth the price. I do not recommend this place. The service time is so slow. Again, the food is not worth the price. I even went to the other branch in Leon Guinto but the line is LONGER so we had to wait because that was the order of our clients and visitors in Lasalle, they already gave the money and are looking forward to it but it turned out the food WAS COLD??? I CAN'T.
